    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Apterolarnaca (Bianigryllacris) biprocera sp. nov. Male: A. head in frontal view; B–C. head and pronotum: B. dorsal view, C. lateral view; D. second and third abdominal tergites in lateral view; F. hind leg in external view; E, G–J. apex of abdomen: E. lateral view, G. dorsal view, H. apical view, I. apical and slightly ventral view, J. ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8345890/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

