    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Apterolarnaca (Bianigryllacris) biprocera sp. nov. Female: A. head in frontal view; B–C. head and pronotum: B. dorsal view, C. lateral view; D. second and third abdominal tergites in lateral view; E. hind leg in external view; F–H. apex of abdomen: F. dorsal view, G. lateral view, H. ventral view." ;
